data.title: Summertime Rendering Vol. 3: Orbital Resonance
data.meta_description: The Hitogashima Summer Festival tragically ended, and July 22nd starts again for the fourth time! Shinpei is now looking for the key character, Ryunosuke Nagamo, that can possibly help him defeat the deadly "Shadows". What secret does Nagamo hold?
